The simulated datasets were generated utilizing the PROSSTT Python package.
The empirical datasets analyzed in this study are publicly accessible from various repositories.
Specifically, the processed human myeloid dataset was retrieved from Figshare https://doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.25243225.
The mouse pancreatic dataset is available for download from the CellEnergy GitHub repository at https://github.com/lhshuang/CellEnergy/blob/main/inst/out/En_Seurat.rds.
The human T cell depleted bone marrow dataset can be accessed from the Gene Expression Omnibus (GEO) database under the accession number GSE200046.
